data.description: Back on the market!!! This classic Maine farmhouse in Unity, Maine comes with so much character and endless possibilities! The home has 2 bedrooms, 1 full bath with laundry, Living room, Kitchen/ Dining space, and a large back deck for entertaining. The 1680 sq foot workshop on a concrete slab was built in 2001, which comes with a half bath & private office space. There is also carport for more storage, and an additional outbuilding. The beautiful 8 acres includes woods with trails, open fields, and possibilities to sub-divide the land. Don't miss your opportunity to own this fantastic property, Call today! Conventional financing or Cash only.
